{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-19", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "遠方星火", "storyInfo": "在一所位於烏薩斯北部小城的大學校園內，塔露拉找到了她一直在找的“人”。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“......接下來，請同學們翻到課本第一百三十二頁。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "泰拉曆31年，駿鷹帝國正式更名為烏薩斯帝國。這段歷史我們已經花了兩堂課來分析和探討。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "學界普遍認為，駿鷹失去君主的資格，其源頭在於統治階層的腐朽與無能，以及代表了社會主要生產力的烏薩斯的崛起。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這場戰爭被描述為烏薩斯的起義，代表了先民對神民權力的挑戰。自此，神民在泰拉諸國都逐漸喪失了盤踞統治地位的正當性。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "然而，當我們換個角度去回顧這場戰爭，很容易就會產生一系列疑問。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在當時的社會情境下，如果佔據統治地位的並非駿鷹，而是另一支烏薩斯，變革是否還會發生？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果身為統治者的駿鷹，並未堅持種族差異政策，不再侵佔烏薩斯的財產，給予烏薩斯同等的升遷機會......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "駿鷹帝國的覆滅是否就能被避免，還是來得更早？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果......當年可汗的騎兵並未踏足這片土地呢？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，你也是來聽卡謝娜老師上課的嗎？", "name": "烏薩斯青年學生"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡謝娜......老師？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，由她負責授課的烏薩斯帝國史一直很受歡迎。", "name": "烏薩斯青年學生"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近總能看到像你一樣的年輕人在走廊旁聽。你不是我們學校的學生，對吧？你看起來不像個大學生。", "name": "烏薩斯青年學生"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實你可以走進去的，卡謝娜老師不介意你們站在教室後面。這樣你會聽得更清楚些。", "name": "烏薩斯青年學生"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了。她的聲音我已經聽得足夠清楚。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好吧，反正這堂課也快結束了。我還有其他課要上，我先走啦。", "name": "烏薩斯青年學生"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請快些離開這裡吧。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“這些問題的答案，你們或許並不能在任何課本上找到。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但我希望你們好好想一想。在吃飯的時候，洗澡的時候，甚至睡覺的時候......讓問題回蕩在自己的大腦裡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當一個念頭徘徊得足夠久，就將它寫下來。我樂於看見你們的觀點。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "好了，這堂課該結束了。在下一次鈴聲響起之前，享受你們短暫的自由吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有什麼疑問嗎，同學？", "name": "駿鷹老師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我找到你了。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她為什麼要進城去？", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了找一個人。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼人值得我們冒這個險？", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九，明明是你說的，我們在烏薩斯的所有行動都不能靠近移動城市。", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不是一直都想審判她嗎？在她開口之前，她還需要找一個答案。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有這個答案，她自己都無法相信自己吐露的字句。那樣的話，我們更無法相信她。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本來就不該相信她！", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一個人進了城，萬一就這樣一走了之呢？我們之前為了救出她而做的一切努力，我們之後關於她的全部計畫，都會付之一炬！", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不會的。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為她自己清楚，她已經無處可去。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，只要你們還信我，我就會向你們保證，無論她去了哪裡，我都能再次把她抓出來。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你......但這是基於你這一年多裡帶著我們做的所有事情。", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和她不一樣，你沒那麼喜歡耍嘴皮子。九，這是我們都很喜歡你的一點。你最好不要把這個好習慣給弄丟了。", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你擔心我會被她影響？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還真有點困難。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_332_1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九，有糾察隊靠近——", "name": "整合運動術師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_332_1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意隱蔽。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和我們預計的一樣。再過半個小時，這條路線就會不再安全。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她最好能及時回來。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為能更早見到你——", "name": "駿鷹老師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——塔露拉。", "name": "駿鷹老師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......卡謝娜。這名字還是這麼直白淺顯啊，科西切。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......名字。名字只是一個稱謂，假如你嫌這些音節會勾起一些不快的回憶，你也可以叫我菲奧莉特。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，你叫什麼我都不關心。你的名字，就如同你的皮囊一樣，沒有讓我記住的價值。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是為何而來呢，塔露拉？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想從我嘴裡得到一個確切的答案嗎？你想聽見我告訴你，是的，科西切已經離開了你，如今的你只是塔露拉？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你會得到你想要的。我現在就可以這麼說，就如你希望聽見的那樣，一字不差。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題是——你願意相信嗎？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想讓我相信一條黑蛇？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的新把戲嗎，科西切？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你給了我足夠多的資訊，好讓我在最短的時間內找到你——我只能認為，你是有意誘使我來到這裡。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你回去看過了？回到我們共同的家？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是我的家。那只是陰謀的發源地，毒蛇們喜愛的老巢。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的說法真令我傷心啊。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你還是讀了我的信件，不是嗎？你始終記得科西切公爵用來接收蛇鱗密信的管道。那些占了公爵領的秘密警察就找不到。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——一封十年前就已寄出的信，寄信人就在這所學校。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都不知該讚歎你的深謀遠慮，還是該慶幸那條管道的確封存了十年，你的蛇鱗們早已朽作塵埃。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領地的荒廢令你感到高興嗎？塔露拉，他們本來能在你的治理下獲得更好的生活，而不是被第四集團軍撕扯得不成模樣。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別裝作你比我更關心他們了。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，是什麼讓你甘願待在這最北邊的小城裡？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科西切，我記得你更喜歡靠南一些的城市。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅因為那裡的空氣更加濕潤，還因為培育了一代又一代權力核心的土壤也更適合你的陰謀滋長。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凍原——凍原就不同了。這裡的人們過得更苦，光是對糧食收成的擔憂就足以占滿他們的大腦。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你引以為豪的演說，於他們而言就像佩在你身上的假花一樣，徒有其表，毫無用處。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉......塔露拉。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#6$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我說，我在這裡，是因為這附近的凍原上有你留下的足跡呢？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我會說你胡說八道。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“人類的歷史，就是鬥爭史。”", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明明都記得的。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些年裡，我教會你的一切，你都用在了你後來的抗爭上。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你都記得，那麼凍原上的感染者鬥士塔露拉，和繼承了公爵之位的塔露拉，對我來說又有多大分別？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你毀掉了我在凍原上建立起的一切。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我毀掉的嗎？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#4$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你心裡，犯下這一系列致命錯誤的，究竟是誰？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#4$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倘若你真認同自己無罪，你根本沒有必要用一年半的時間去思考自己該選擇何種方式的死亡。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會轉頭就投入下一場轟轟烈烈的抗爭中。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉，我知道你為什麼要來到我面前。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要用對我的審判來審判你自己，你想聽見我的懺悔從而開始你的懺悔。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要的——不過是一點可憐的心理安慰。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說下去。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓我說下去？我還以為——", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我會讓你看見我的怒火？不，科西切，你還不配。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到目前為止，你說的每一句話，都曾在我的腦海中預演過。一年半並不是一段很短的時間，而被關在羅德島上的我確實無事可做。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想從我手中活下去，你還需要說一些更新鮮的。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，看得出來，那段自我監禁的時光讓你變得更有耐心了。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我提起凍原，並不是為了刺痛你。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉......看看這所學校吧。看看那些學生臉上的神采。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們相信五月的陽光會融化凍原上的冰雪，也相信著比凍原還硬的烏薩斯會在他們腳下改變。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你又想用你那些齷齪的思想，去玷污他們的天真？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我是想在他們之中尋找下一個繼承人？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，塔露拉，我只是一名普普通通的大學老師而已。我傳遞的只有知識和思想，並沒有任何權力或者財富握在我的手裡。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如他們想要權力，他們可以自己用雙手去爭取。假如他們渴望陰謀，他們同樣能從我傳授的知識裡找到最合適的技巧。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想讓我相信——你在我身上遭遇的失敗，竟然讓你一蹶不振、秉性大改？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失敗？我從來不認為那是失敗。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#9$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整合運動並沒有徹底毀在切爾諾伯格核心城，科西切的計畫也一樣。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#9$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，你們暫時阻止了科西切，他沒能等來他想要的那場足以立刻改變烏薩斯的戰爭。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#9$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但烏薩斯還是步上了科西切為她設定的軌道。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭正在發生。議會和軍隊的摩擦依然升級了，人們的意志也在一場又一場衝突中碰撞出新的火花。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，我會站在最富有活力的土壤上，盡我所能地播撒種子。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我將引導......或者說促成這些變革的發生。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你向我否認過教育大眾的意義。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當事態發生了變化，一位統治者卻依舊按照過去的方法行事，那他必然會走向毀滅。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依然......以統治者自居。我明白了，你其實一點都沒有改變。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差點忘了，你痛恨這個詞語，就跟你厭恨科西切的控制一樣。我早就告訴過你，我並不在乎誰來統治。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從烏薩斯從駿鷹手中奪下這片土地，權力的更迭在明裡暗中發生過多少次？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉，你就是我，我也是你。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們想要的，都是烏薩斯仍能在我們掌心迸出星火。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場火......早晚會點燃整個烏薩斯。不，不僅烏薩斯。維多利亞......還有其他國家，都會被捲進來。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#8$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大火過後，這片土地會變得更加繁榮，還是迎來毀滅？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烏薩斯走過了自己的第一個千年——而我會令它走向第二個，第三個。這才是黑蛇存在的意義。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#8$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑蛇不死，不是因為我有著自我存續的意志，而是因為烏薩斯必須活下去。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_236", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯蘭的王嗣已經回到了倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看樣子是的。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是薩卡茲有意贈送給我們的消息，作為我們先前送回那幾名薩卡茲信使的回報。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_236"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回報？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們不過是希望借我們的手，讓公爵之間的爭鬥進一步升級。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顯而易見。但從他們的做法中，我們也能看出來，倫蒂尼姆城內的局勢又起了變化，薩卡茲有些著急。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_236"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲還說了什麼嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼有用的了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#5"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，自從“間諜”暴露，我們能收到的倫蒂尼姆的消息變少了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#5"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_236"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊......真可惜。好在我們的損失還在可控範圍內。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#2"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，還有另一條可能很重要的消息。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這條消息是一位與我們合作的哥倫比亞軍火商透露的——", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個月前，那支名為整合運動的隊伍迎回了他們之前的“領袖”。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_236"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_236"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是之前的情報全部屬實的話，她......她很有可能也是德拉克呀。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真、真的嗎？你你你沒騙我？！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#5"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我騙你這個幹什麼？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#5"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打我一拳吧。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#5"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你發什麼神經？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#5"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你快打我一拳，不然我真的以為自己是在做夢！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#4"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然你撞個牆試試？不過，不要花太大力氣，撞破了別人家牆壁的話，你還得花時間跟這個郡的騎警解釋。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#4"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我一時間都不知道該說什麼......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#3"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真這麼驚訝？天天念叨著隊長肯定沒死的人明明是你。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#3"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我還以為......還以為......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以為她還在哪裡等著你去救她？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是知道隊長逃出來了，果然還是更加驚喜啊！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，陳陳，沒有你，我就不可能認識羅德島的人，我沒有加入羅德島，他們也不會幫我救出隊長，太好了，嗚嗚嗚......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#2"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別抱上來！", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚，可是我好高興！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1#6"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少......別那麼大力氣......呃唔......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1#6"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，陳陳，那......那你是不是就要走了？你答應了要幫我救隊長，而現在隊長已經不需要我去救了......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種時候，你的腦子倒是轉得挺快。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實話說，我不是沒想過。在得知她逃出了羅德島以後，我一直在考慮去找她。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，我能看出來的......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_010_chen_1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但陳暉潔從來不是半途而廢的人。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走了這麼久，我們好不容易得到了一些線索。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛，我會幫你繼續追查下去。“等到鬼魂部隊重新暴露在陽光下的那一天”——我會去做我早就該做的事。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會去找塔露拉。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "char_010_chen_1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔露拉，用上科西切教會你的所有技巧，看一看吧，看看我說的這些話是不是都發自真心。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必了。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還想著在這裡殺死我嗎？為了躲開城內衛兵的視線，你沒有拿劍。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只能用你的火焰處死我。你是想在這些喜愛著我的學生面前......犯下這樣恐怖的罪行嗎？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要殺死你，我還不至於會驚動別人。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，科西切，這也是你教會我的知識。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死我......就能令你滿意嗎？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如你並不能感到滿足，我還能給你第二個名字，甚至第三個。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#5$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是想告訴我，在烏薩斯境內的黑蛇，還不止你一個。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也能當作是我為了活下去而設法欺騙你。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#2$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的新軀體......很脆弱。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死你，並不比殺死那個老斐迪亞要難。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還等什麼？快，讓我的軀體化作灰燼......灑滿這昏暗的走廊！", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“恐怖的感染者劊子手再現大學校園”——這會是第二天的報紙頭條。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......不會在意這些惡名。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順帶一提，我也不怕三分鐘之後就會趕到這裡的糾察隊。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......你那些守在城外的新老朋友......他們還不是皇帝內衛的對手。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便他們在一些掌權者的授意下，暫且容忍你回到烏薩斯......也絕對不會允許你在烏薩斯境內殺人。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......科西切。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得，要是內衛們知道不死的怪物——切爾諾伯格事件的主謀就在這裡，比起抓住我，他們會不會先把視線和刀刃一起投向你？", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，你為何還不動手？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#7$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......時間快到了。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還沒回來？九，你是不是看錯她了？", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一到了約定時間，她真的沒有出現，你們就按原計劃撤退。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_016"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？", "name": "整合運動戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_016"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還戴著我的鐐銬，那她就是我的犯人。我會親手把她捉拿歸案。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那你可以省點力氣了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——塔露拉。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回來了，而且一分鐘都沒有遲到。你見完你要見的人了？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以呢？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會是想讓我談談收獲吧？我本來不打算讓那些又臭又長的絮叨污染你的耳朵。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不錯，你精神了不少，都會開玩笑了。", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個惡神呢？你成功殺死他了嗎？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說她不再是那個人了。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你相信？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不信。但我也不再是那個以為殺了她就能解決問題的塔露拉。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會允許她離開我的視線。有必要的時候，我會立刻動手。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我總有一種預感......", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "預感？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不死的惡神......終將死去。可殺死她的，不會是我。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——烏薩斯會殺死她。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她至今仍以為自己能操弄人們的意志，而我們會證明給她看——", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終有一天，覺醒的人們會將愚昧的統治者狠狠地拋下。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，烏薩斯將再無黑蛇。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在呢？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，在最終回到這裡之前，我們先去一趟維多利亞。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_043_1#2", "name2": "char_011_talula_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於決定與我們同行了？", "name": "九"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_043_1#2"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_011_talula_1#3"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是你的囚犯，除了跟著你們，我無處可去。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且是你說的......那裡的感染者，正在等我們。", "name": "塔露拉"}, "figure_art": "char_011_talula_1#3"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}